text: Sara Gjoni (born in Tirana) a is model and beauty pageant contestant. She won the title of Miss Albania in 2011 and represented Albania at Miss Model of the World in 2011. She won the title Miss Bikini in 2011. She also won title miss model of the best talent in dance. ==References== ==Other websites== * Kruja pret Miss Shqipërinë, Sara Gjoni shpallet “Miss Bikini 2011?
